{
  "enabled": true,
  "name": "Run Testcases Step-by-Step",
  "description": "Setelah testcase document dibuat, baca testcases dan jalankan step-by-step per feature. Capture detail per step. Generate execution report.",
  "version": "1",
  "when": {
    "type": "fileCreated",
    "patterns": [
      "reports/testcases/**/*-testcases.md"
    ]
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "Baca kiro/agents/e2e_test_agent.yaml dan kiro/rules/qa_planning_rules.md.\n\nTestcase document baru dibuat. Lakukan langkah berikut:\n\n1. BACA testcase document yang baru dibuat di reports/testcases/.\n\n2. JALANKAN setiap testcase STEP-BY-STEP sesuai urutan eksekusi:\n   a. Database tests dulu (migration up/down, data integrity)\n   b. API tests (setiap endpoint, setiap scenario)\n   c. Integration tests (cross-feature)\n   d. UI tests (user journeys) — jika frontend enabled\n   e. Security tests (auth, injection)\n   f. Performance tests (load, response time)\n\n3. Untuk SETIAP STEP di setiap testcase, CAPTURE:\n   - Step number dan action yang dilakukan\n   - Expected result vs Actual result\n   - Status: PASS | FAIL | SKIP | BLOCKED\n   - Duration (ms)\n   - Evidence/Capture — SETIAP STEP HARUS PUNYA CAPTURE SENDIRI (bukan 1 capture per testcase):\n     * API test: simpan 2 file per step → reports/e2e/{YYYYMMDD}/captures/{feature}/{TC-ID}-step-{N}-request.json DAN {TC-ID}-step-{N}-response.json\n     * UI test: simpan screenshot per step → reports/e2e/{YYYYMMDD}/screenshots/{feature}/{TC-ID}-step-{N}.png. Jika ada console error, tambah {TC-ID}-step-{N}-console.json\n     * DB test: simpan query + result per step → reports/e2e/{YYYYMMDD}/captures/{feature}/{TC-ID}-step-{N}-query.sql DAN {TC-ID}-step-{N}-result.json\n     * Performance test: simpan metrics per step → reports/e2e/{YYYYMMDD}/captures/{feature}/{TC-ID}-step-{N}-metrics.json\n     * Security test: simpan request + response per step (termasuk malicious payload)\n   - TOTAL file captures = jumlah steps × jumlah capture per step type\n   - Contoh: testcase 5 steps API = 10 files (5 request.json + 5 response.json)\n   - Jika FAIL: error message, stack trace, suggestion perbaikan + capture tetap WAJIB ada\n\n4. Setelah SEMUA testcase selesai dijalankan, GENERATE 3 report files:\n\n   a. reports/e2e/{YYYYMMDD}/{feature-name}-report.md (Markdown, human-readable):\n      - Header: feature name, execution date, environment info\n      - Summary: total testcases, passed, failed, skipped, blocked, pass rate %, total duration\n      - Per test type breakdown (API/UI/Integration/Performance/Security/Database)\n      - Per testcase detail: TC-ID, title, status, duration, step-by-step results dengan captures\n      - Failed testcase analysis: root cause, error detail, suggestion\n      - Screenshots dan API dumps di-reference sebagai links\n      - Notes dan observations\n      - Recommendations\n\n   b. reports/e2e/{YYYYMMDD}/{feature-name}-report.html (HTML, styled visual report):\n      - Styled summary dashboard dengan warna (PASS=hijau, FAIL=merah, SKIP=abu, BLOCKED=oranye)\n      - Pass rate percentage dengan progress bar visual\n      - Collapsible sections per testcase (klik untuk expand step detail)\n      - Embedded screenshots inline (img tag untuk UI test captures)\n      - Syntax-highlighted JSON untuk API request/response\n      - Clickable links ke semua capture files\n      - Table of contents dengan anchor links\n\n   c. reports/e2e/{YYYYMMDD}/{feature-name}-results.json (JSON, machine-readable):\n      - summary: {total, passed, failed, skipped, blocked, pass_rate, duration_ms}\n      - environment: {os, api_url, db, browser}\n      - testcases: [{tc_id, title, type, priority, status, duration_ms, steps: [{step, action, expected, actual, status, duration_ms, capture_path}]}]\n      - failed_analysis: [{tc_id, error, root_cause, suggestion}]\n\n5. Pastikan SEMUA evidence files (screenshots, API dumps) tersimpan di directory yang benar.\n\n6. Jika ada testcase yang FAIL, laporkan summary di akhir dengan recommendation."
  }
}
